data.name: richTextBox1.Text
data.value: Usage Information - Double-click list items to enable, disable, or delete them. - Add folders to delete via the "FOLDERS (+)" button. - Add scripts for parallel execution via the "CMDS (+)" button. - Click "LAUNCH" to review deletion settings and start the process. - For emergency situations, activate the music feature as a covert signal-it plays during deletion and alerts you discreetly by stop when finished. - Use this software at your own risk.
